"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        No specific treatment",
"       </td>",
"      </tr>",
"      <tr>",
"       <td>",
"        GSD I (MIM #232200; GSD Ia, von Gierke disease, glucose-6-phosphatase deficiency; GSD Ib, c, and d due to transport defects)",
